Ext.data.JsonP['Titanium_Modules']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Titanium Modules</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083140\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Titanium Modules</h1>\n    <p>Titanium provides the ability to extend its built-in functionality through a series of optional extensions, called Titanium+Plus Modules. We&apos;ll reference them as Modules here. This guide covers how to create a new module inside Studio, and how to use that module in a project. For more in-depth information about programming a module, see the <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/iOS_Module_Development_Guide\">iOS Module Development Guide</a> and <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Android_Module_Development_Guide\">Android Module Development Guide</a>.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083140_TitaniumModules-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Creating_a_New_Titanium_Module\">Creating a New Titanium Module</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Using_Titanium_Modules\">Using Titanium Modules</a>    </p>\n</li></ul><ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Windows_Module_Development_Guide\">Windows Module Development Guide</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083140\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Titanium Modules"});